Instruction: Put the pear, bananas, and the apple on the kitchentable.
Put the toothpaste, toothbrush, and towel on the bathroomcabinet.
Put the notes, the magazine, and the book on the desk.
Put the washingsponge, dishbowl, the plate, and the dishwashingliquid in the sink.
Put the crackers, the pudding, the cupcake, and creamybuns on the kitchencounter.
Put the mouse on the mousemat, and the toy on the nightstand.
Put the pillow on the bed, the coffeepot on the coffeetable, and the towel on the towelrack.
Put the carrot on the cuttingboard, the barsoap and the facecream on the bathroomcounter, and the candle on the tvstand.
Put the remotecontrol on the chair, the fryingpan on the stove, and the clock on the nightstand.
Put the creamybuns in the plate, and put the plate and milk together on the kitchentable.
Put the chicken and the peach in the fridge and make sure it's turned on.
Put the remotecontrol on the sofa, turn on the TV, and put the clothespants in the closet.
Put the clothespile in the washingmachine, turn it on, then make sure the cellphone is on and charging.
Put the milk in the microwave to heat up and put the breadslice on the kitchentable.
Organize the paper and put it in the folder, then put the book on the desk and open it.
Put the pancake in the fryingpan and place the fryingpan on the stove to heat up.
Put the hairproduct, the facecream, and the barsoap in the bathroomcabinet and turn on the radio.
Put the plate and the dishbowl in the dishwasher to clean and turn on the lightswitch.
Turn off the tv, turn on the computer, open the curtains, and make sure the mouse and keyboard are plugged in.
Close the curtains, turn on the tablelamp, and switch on the clock.
Use the papertowel to wipe the kitchencabinet, and then throw the used papertowel into the garbagecan.
Turn on the lightswitch, and then use the rag to clean the wallpictureframe, towelrack, and bookshelf.
Take the rag to the sink to clean it, and then use it to wipe the desk.
Take the apple to the faucet, wash it clean, cut them into slices, put them on the plate, and place the plate on the coffeetable.
Use the duster to remove dust from the rug, unplug the toaster, and clean it with the rag.
Use a brush to clean the remote control, picture frame, and clock, then wipe down the TV stand with a cloth
Cut the chicken and the carrot into pieces, place them on the oventray, season with the condimentbottle.
Wash the apples and plums, slice the apples with the kitchenknife, and place the apples neatly on the cutting board.
Put the clothespile in the sink to wash it, and then use the rag to clean the sink.
